                <note rend="inline" type="source">837.513/54: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Representative on Special Mission in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Crowder</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-07-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 5, 1922</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>39. Your 41, June 30, 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department desires to commend you for the admirable way in which you have handled
                    the negotiations and for the results obtained.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
